{"tid":851192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"YG逼Winner驗尿、南太鉉比中指不屑說：比陌生人還不如","createTime":"2018-10-07T03:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T06:23:38.000Z","uid":88491,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e07d38a142828cddcc72b0d6aff9717a36107899","tid":851192,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:18:53.000Z","msg":"《YG戰資》主軸設定為情境喜劇，講述BIGBANG勝利被降職到「YG戰略資料本部」（簡稱YG戰資），為了重新獲得公司代表的喜愛，拚了命努力重振。為了這個節目，YG旗下藝人全員參與演出，連已經離開公司的朴春、前Winner成員南太鉉都被找回來，果然在播出之後造成話題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/111436_538d1b5b36712d29eb33a1016fa686ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F111436_538d1b5b36712d29eb33a1016fa686ff.png&h=6db91676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲劇本中，南太鉉被介紹為iKON前成員，還有比中指畫面。<br />\n然而，節目中，南太鉉出場時，勝利的台詞卻是「這是我們iKON的前成員」，被旁人糾正後，才改為「Winner的前成員」。此外，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">劇情設定南太鉉被找回來參加家族活動，但他以不屑表情說「家人太久不見的話，比陌生人還不如，甚至現在也不是家人」，最後還對鏡頭比了個中指。</span></strong>雖然只是劇本設定，卻讓粉絲看得十分心疼，認為南太鉉是遭到節目利用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/07/111551_87d574ca72ad840f00a3de4bba152c44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F07%2F111551_87d574ca72ad840f00a3de4bba152c44.png&h=873208be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《YG戰資》要Winner驗尿惹火粉絲。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n另外，《YG戰資》也把YG藝人數次陷入染毒風波的爭議事件拿來自嘲<span style=\"color: red;\">，<strong>節目中有段情節便是要Winner驗髮、驗尿，藉以證明YG是個乾淨的公司</strong></span>。不過，Winner過去並未扯上毒品爭議，如今被要求演出這樣的情節，令粉絲非常氣憤，許多人痛罵「以為節目是為了宣傳，結果卻是這樣」、「不要再消費Winner了」、「公司形象真的要毀了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink : <a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1275235#ixzz5TDAAjONO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1275235%23ixzz5TDAAjONO&d=VXAYx0S8Fq2ve3j0i6Iwn9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f248523a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1275235#ixzz5TDAAjONO</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">YG 又做乜尻野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f5ef8e56ced9594e4ccd7cebcb2e86ca601940a9","tid":851192,"uid":88491,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"諗策劃條友係咪食左屎"},{"pid":"e7b5c4a22f4bc31a343d3a7d1ca25db8292e9eb5","tid":851192,"uid":68661,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f5ef8e56ced9594e4ccd7cebcb2e86ca601940a9","tid":851192,"uid":88491,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"諗策劃條友係咪食左屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"楊菊花點解重未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8ab217a7ec8ed2bd728de4ea61dcdbb002aafb","tid":851192,"uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7b5c4a22f4bc31a343d3a7d1ca25db8292e9eb5","tid":851192,"uid":68661,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f5ef8e56ced9594e4ccd7cebcb2e86ca601940a9","tid":851192,"uid":88491,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"諗策劃條友係咪食左屎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"楊菊花點解重未死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:09:15.000Z","msg":"真係越黎越on9"},{"pid":"f8718607a49b328cb7129f6790eb42cf97d29990","tid":851192,"uid":130950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:14:54.000Z","msg":"YG已完"},{"pid":"eb3ea5c760332025f0c21c5d867f7e51d6c0b1f6","tid":851192,"uid":68661,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"8e8ab217a7ec8ed2bd728de4ea61dcdbb002aafb","tid":851192,"uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7b5c4a22f4bc31a343d3a7d1ca25db8292e9eb5","tid":851192,"uid":68661,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f5ef8e56ced9594e4ccd7cebcb2e86ca601940a9","tid":851192,"uid":88491,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T03:58: